### 1. Timeline-Based Movement Architecture

The movement animation system in `ALFPTacticsUnit` uses the following pattern:

**Timeline Setup (BeginPlay, lines 88-98 of LFPTacticsUnit.cpp):**
```cpp
if (MoveCurve)
